@{i}Description@{ui}
     This sends TextureStudio's main screen to the back.

@{i}Parameters@{ui}
     None.

@{i}Returns@{ui}
     Nothing.

@{i}Errors@{ui}
     rc = 0 if the operation was successful.

     rc = 10 if the operation failed for any reason, rc2 will contain a
     string describing the problem.

@{i}Example@{ui}
     The following sends TextureStudio's screen to the back.

          SCREEN_BACK

@{i}Known bugs@{ui}
     None.

     See @{"SCREEN_FRONT" Link "SCREEN_FRONT"}.


@EndNode

@Node "SCREEN_FRONT" "TextureStudio.guide/SCREEN_FRONT"
